# LN1 open source linear to alternative

## General
**url** https://ln1.one

## Stack
- **Bun** as main runtime, sql queries, package manager
- **Supabase** for authentication

## Process
- Read src/app.config.ts for available configuration 

## Features

### Issues

**Assignee**
Each issue can have a user assigned to it. By default, an issue is unassigned.

When the assignee of an issue changes, the new assignee should receive an email via Resend.
The email must contain a link to the issue.
